Scuse-me, I wanted to thank Xemnes...

It works now: I succeeded by stopping the remaining automaticly starting services: "MSSQL$SONY_MEDIAMGR", and "SQLAgent$SONY_MEDIAMGR", using "Autoruns". Then I renamed the "Sony Shared Plug-In" sx86 folder. Then I could patch teh new installed Vegas. Then it works.
I THINK YOU NEED ABSOLUTELY NO SONY AGENT RUNNING AT INSTALLATION TIME.
I hope this can help someone...
